### 用户管理接口（RBAC）

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 分页查询用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "keyword": "",
  "status": null,
  "roleId": null
}

### 获取用户详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 分配角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/1/assign-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roleIds": [1, 2]
}

### 重置密码
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/1/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 更新用户状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/1/status?status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 编辑用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "newusername",
  "email": "newemail@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 删除用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rbac/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

